| `componentsPremium` | Calculates premium for component-type items with block discounts | Clear. Good. |
| `componentBlockPremium` | Calculates premium for a group of same-type components | Clear. Good. |
| `countByType` | Counts component items by type | Clear. Good. |
| `itemPremiumWithModifiers` | Calculates an item's premium including cursed/enchantment modifiers | Clear and descriptive. Good. |
| `itemBasePremium` | Gets the base premium for an item type | Clear. Good. |
| `isComponent` | Checks if an item is a component type | Clear. Good. |
| `regularItems` | Filters to non-component items | Clear. Good. |

All names are reasonably clear and descriptive. No critical naming issues.

